name: Satellite Synchron
desc: If a monster(s) is Special Summoned from your GY (except during the Damage Step): You can Special Summon this card from your hand. If a Synchro Monster(s) with "Warrior", "Synchron", and/or "Stardust" in its original name is on your field and/or in your GY: You can make this card's Level become 4 until the end of this turn. You can only use each effect of "Satellite Synchron" once per turn.
